  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sofia airport: SOF Connect equity</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project involves an equity co-investment via Meridiam Co-Investment  Infrastructure Eastern Europe SLP managed by Meridiam SAS (&quot;Meridiam&quot;) to  acquire an indirect minority equity stake in SOF Connect AD (the &quot;Company&quot;), a  limited liability company established in Bulgaria for the purposes of  operations and management of Sofia Airport on the basis of the Concession  agreement with the Government. The investment is alongside Meridiam  Infrastructure Europe III and Meridiam Infrastructure Eastern Europe III  (&quot;Meridiam Funds&quot;), which are already indirect shareholders of the Company.</narrative>
  </description>
